{"tid":1092998,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【最輕時140磅】袁偉豪齋飲咖啡填肚 減磅致肌肉萎縮","createTime":"2019-04-05T09:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T02:05:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"89ba20b88b5f7948e363348cb903309b8f8106a9","tid":1092998,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"袁偉豪（Ben）今日到商台接受鄭裕玲訪問，宣傳現正播出的新劇，並表示今次劇集對自己很大挑戰，因為要減磅演出：「希望做到一個好瘦好憔悴嘅感覺，而且又有唔少動作場面，所以真係好大挑戰。」他透露最瘦時只得140磅：「中學之後都未試過跌到呢個磅數，每日淨係飲咖啡，嘢都好少食，希望做到的肌肉萎縮晒、好瘦嗰種感覺。」<br />\n雖然辛苦但他表示其實有點享受：「係有少少變態，到煞科嗰日開始我照鏡，先開始發現自己隻眼同個嘴好突，真係開始有呢個感覺，可惜已經煞咗科，如果可以再早少少開始做效果應該會更好。」他透露減磅期間嘗試在屋企附近跑步，不過因減磅過度跑到半路開始見頭暈：「要即刻同女朋友講，叫佢屋企整定嘢食，我要行返嚟，真係頂唔順。」又稱女友張寶兒十分支持他的決定：「我希望可以喺工作上做多啲突破 ，如果下次有需要增磅我都願意。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190405/large/1554454467_33ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554454467_33ad.jpg&h=dc5116e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190405/large/1554454467_ea8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F1554454467_ea8d.jpg&h=2f4aa0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190405/59453855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F59453855&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJwCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=6e805cc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F59453855&h=cca282b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190405/59453855</a>"},{"pid":"d70fe0c836b874fd94f07eab4f4a7b9fc2f567d2","tid":1092998,"uid":224533,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:32:51.000